data.description: Welcome to this lovely Harker Heights home that is perfect for a large family. The home features 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, and a spacious floor plan with split bedrooms. In addition to the typical living areas, there is a formal dining room that would be ideal for hosting. The kitchen features modern stainless-steel appliances and granite countertops.  The Eat-In Kitchen makes it simple to get everything on the table. Conveniently located near Ft. Cavazos, schools, dining and shopping centers.  Come see this wonderful home today!
